description:
N.O.R.E and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. On this episode the Champs chop it up with fan favorite and Miami Legend Trick Daddy Dollars. They talk about Love and Hip Hop Miami , new ventures and are later joined by co star Veronica Vega.
